snippet.title: Disney Crossy Road | Official Trailer | Available to Download for Free Now
snippet.description:
Why should the chicken get all the fun? Discover an all-new epic, 8-bit endless adventure with Disney Crossy Road, brought to you by Australian game developers, Hipster Whale.

Play with over 100+ of your favorite figurines from Mickey & Friends, Toy Story, The Lion King, Big Hero 6, and more!
See how far you can get by hopping, dodging, and sliding your way through busy lanes of traffic!

Play as Mickey, Donald, Buzz Lightyear, Rapunzel, Mufasa, Sadness, Wreck-It Ralph, Madame Leota, and more of your Disney favorites (many with fun surprises)!

Available to download for free from the App Store and Play Store today! 

App Store: http://bit.ly/DisneyCrossyRoadAppStore
Play Store: http://bit.ly/DisneyCrossyRoadPlayStore
